// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1352 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 1fcf5d94-a021-5edf-b648-f17a1756a9d9

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:17.04*")
